              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                " Ten packages of high or ultra-high purity metal foils",
                " for chromium and indium, alloy foils for manganese,",
                " oxide powder for scandium.",
                " Sizes of samples 0.5mm thick x10mm x20mm except for",
                " chromium -2mm thick x3mm x20mm, and for",
                " niobium 0.2mm thick x10mm x20mm.",
                " Were set around the neutron source at 5 cm from",
                " the target in angular range from 0 to 140 deg covering",
                " incident neutron energies from 19 to 12 MeV."
              ]
            }
          ],
